|commander2=[[Archduke Charles, Duke of Teschen|Archduke Charles]]
|strength1=40,000 soldiers
|strength2=80,000 soldiers
|casualties1=400 killed, 1600 wounded, 2,000 captured, 1 gun lost.<ref>Smith, p. 148.</ref>
